Diego Simeone's side beat their cross-town rivals 1-0 at Vicente Calderon thanks to Mario Mandzukic's goal after a 1-1 draw at the Santiago Bernabeu in the first leg.

Mundo Deportivo and AS lead both lead with the headline 'Supercampeon' with a picture of Atletico celebrating their success while Marca hailed them as a 'super team'.

Both defending champions Atletico Madrid and Champions League winners Real Madrid will kick off their La Liga campaign on Monday while Barcelona begin their season against Elche at the Nou Camp on Sunday.

